flavor_text_entries.red:
It spits out
POISONPOWDER to
immobilize the enemy and then
finishes it with
a spray of ACID.
flavor_text_entries.blue:
It spits out
POISONPOWDER to
immobilize the enemy and then
finishes it with
a spray of ACID.
flavor_text_entries.yellow:
When hungry, it
swallows anything
that moves. Its hapless prey is
melted inside by
strong acids.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
Even though it is
filled with ACID,
it does not melt because it also
oozes a neutral­
izing fluid.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
If its prey is
bigger than its
mouth, it slices up the victim with
sharp leaves, then
eats every morsel.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
When it's hungry,
it swings its
razor-sharp leaves, slicing up
any unlucky object
nearby for food.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
WEEPINBELL has a large hook on its rear
end. At night, the POKéMON hooks on to
a tree branch and goes to sleep. If it moves around in its sleep, it may
wake up to find itself on the ground.

flavor_text_entries.emerald:
At night, a WEEPINBELL hangs on to a tree
branch with its hooked rear and sleeps.
If it moves around in its sleep, it may
wake up to find itself on the ground.
flavor_text_entries.firered:
The leafy parts act as cutters for
slashing foes. It spits a fluid that
dissolves everything.
